Detailed Description

template<unsigned DIM>
class PlaneBoundaryCondition< DIM >

A plane cell population boundary condition class, which stops nodes moving through a specified plane in the domain.

Todo:
The naming of this class indicates that it is specific to 3D (see #1589)
